{"tid":334471,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無新界人打算去元朗yoho 睇imax?","createTime":"2017-07-24T17:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T08:42:14.000Z","uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8bfe8c221d7d6e776b0d006e727b550c2cbdb2","tid":334471,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"諗住去睇鄧寇克imax，好似平過出面，唔知係咪新開，之前冇睇過imax, 唔識分定差，有無巴打去過可以分享下？"},{"pid":"7caf19b6f4990577dd476906acb29171d53fde97","tid":334471,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"門口好多農夫賣庶賣生果，上次睇睇吓戲仲有隻牛衝咗入嚟"},{"pid":"31ef6a5bf56bf1b4e01ec5bc609fa972800fa82a","tid":334471,"uid":2483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門口好多農夫賣庶賣生果，上次睇睇吓戲仲有隻牛衝咗入嚟</blockquote><br />\n你真係好撚風趣嘅姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b2ed02573f58c3a140cc8cbc5bc56c765f2a59","tid":334471,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門口好多農夫賣庶賣生果，上次睇睇吓戲仲有隻牛衝咗入嚟</blockquote><br />\n好撚幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d452055719f12546b0060be203066486707ef2cb","tid":334471,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門口好多農夫賣庶賣生果，上次睇睇吓戲仲有隻牛衝咗入嚟</blockquote><br />\n嗯"},{"pid":"8308f41b874d729164c4b59ff2d901e9ae005cbf","tid":334471,"uid":18082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門口好多農夫賣庶賣生果，上次睇睇吓戲仲有隻牛衝咗入嚟</blockquote><br />\n今時今日重有人講埋啲遠古笑話<br />\n<br />\n柒到無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88203a55a5d57294a010d2ac6cc78b04c0694f2a","tid":334471,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:42:07.000Z","msg":"無（新東撚）"},{"pid":"70796b63ba64292b1be565df6ac37feb2a7ead1c","tid":334471,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>門口好多農夫賣庶賣生果，上次睇睇吓戲仲有隻牛衝咗入嚟</blockquote><br />\n今時今日重有人講埋啲遠古笑話<br />\n<br />\n柒到無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尷尬feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281681c2cdc07649c730106411292ec02c4dd40f","tid":334471,"uid":5006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住去睇鄧寇克imax，好似平過出面，唔知係咪新開，之前冇睇過imax, 唔識分定差，有無巴打去過可以分享下？</blockquote><br />\n睇左 平過出面好多<br />\n我第一日去 夜晚場都係$100<br />\n<br />\n早點去買飛否則會無晒靚位<br />\n我都係睇鄧寇克 音響係幾好 <br />\n但唔好預期有震撼場面睇 因為sell氣氛同劇情多<br />\n而劇情好唔好睇見人見致 出面都有幾個罵戰post<br />\n<br />\n另外坐得好舒服 又闊落 冷氣幾凍 可考慮帶多件褸去"},{"pid":"44f763ad722d8599d07f0d5d4a905535c6bcfe36","tid":334471,"uid":31111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"想知個moon size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560fcfbceee781bbd5df6419b69e81c5c1959169","tid":334471,"uid":7452,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知個moon size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/144144_02fd0a05069823198265b640dd68aee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F144144_02fd0a05069823198265b640dd68aee9.jpg&h=de9dd540&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d03757acdfd3804efce48433f4068d7ff9586f9","tid":334471,"uid":22554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"本身住元朗, 以前新元朗中心仲有百老匯個陣都完全唔會想係元朗睇戲<br />\n<br />\n元朗睇戲的人質素係極差, <br />\n<br />\n大聲傾計, 傾電話, 依D 野係以前係層出不窮<br />\n<br />\n當然, 近年多左新樓, 多左外面D 人搬入來會變成點真係唔知"},{"pid":"2bedf4d74fbf611143a4a4a3632ba16d4e7a9719","tid":334471,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"聽講成地瓜子，污糟邋遢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b849b5246e947c7b5c55d1597ec4a22351d02934","tid":334471,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知個moon size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/144144_02fd0a05069823198265b640dd68aee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F144144_02fd0a05069823198265b640dd68aee9.jpg&h=de9dd540&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈哈哈"},{"pid":"8255cc71e4cd7d1565cf21461e81134619e0a31d","tid":334471,"uid":115250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知個moon size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/144144_02fd0a05069823198265b640dd68aee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F144144_02fd0a05069823198265b640dd68aee9.jpg&h=de9dd540&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nMoon size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638f5254d00278fcea1c1701cb020db160dfe0a6","tid":334471,"uid":48460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身住元朗, 以前新元朗中心仲有百老匯個陣都完全唔會想係元朗睇戲<br />\n<br />\n元朗睇戲的人質素係極差, <br />\n<br />\n大聲傾計, 傾電話, 依D 野係以前係層出不窮<br />\n<br />\n當然, 近年多左新樓, 多左外面D 人搬入來會變成點真係唔知</blockquote><br />\n同意 無乜必要都唔想係元朗睇<br />\n雖然香港人普遍都叫無品 係好多區睇戲都被搔擾過<br />\n但零零舍舍係啲牛屎佬未撚進化咁 額頭擺明寫住賤格兩個字"},{"pid":"6e00dbcf32358c48c489aaaaf2c8b1448fa6076a","tid":334471,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身住元朗, 以前新元朗中心仲有百老匯個陣都完全唔會想係元朗睇戲<br />\n<br />\n元朗睇戲的人質素係極差, <br />\n<br />\n大聲傾計, 傾電話, 依D 野係以前係層出不窮<br />\n<br />\n當然, 近年多左新樓, 多左外面D 人搬入來會變成點真係唔知</blockquote><br />\n同意 無乜必要都唔想係元朗睇<br />\n雖然香港人普遍都叫無品 係好多區睇戲都被搔擾過<br />\n但零零舍舍係啲牛屎佬未撚進化咁 額頭擺明寫住賤格兩個字</blockquote><br />\n星期六睇完早場，70蚊平撚到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇野喎，全場觀眾都幾靜下，同去isquare機場睇差唔多<br />\n同埋座位夠闊，行與行之間有好多空位，伸直對腳都踢唔到前面張櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2182da8cbfcc9ce796b370c17254c95879edc766","tid":334471,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"早幾日睇完,幾正<br />\n同ISQUARE好似,但舒服過ISQUARE,成個場D人都靜無人嘈"},{"pid":"438189f9b3fbcbc67a3a6c7514f1b23e876f713e","tid":334471,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9358af20a37f31ecff302c04e05d17f7f89d882","tid":334471,"uid":29317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日睇完,幾正<br />\n同ISQUARE好似,但舒服過ISQUARE,成個場D人都靜無人嘈</blockquote><br />\n唔論觀眾，設備嘅質素邊間好d？"},{"pid":"5123469d9ee467c657baf5045f5494c5c5d3f60a","tid":334471,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日睇完,幾正<br />\n同ISQUARE好似,但舒服過ISQUARE,成個場D人都靜無人嘈</blockquote><br />\n唔論觀眾，設備嘅質素邊間好d？</blockquote><br />\n唔識分 差唔多"},{"pid":"b42177898c846b2204b3217c2dbf001c6e229571","tid":334471,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早幾日睇完,幾正<br />\n同ISQUARE好似,但舒服過ISQUARE,成個場D人都靜無人嘈</blockquote><br />\n唔論觀眾，設備嘅質素邊間好d？</blockquote><br />\n螢幕感覺差唔多大<br />\n但係個場細啲，距離近咗，冇isquare前面咁大截空位<br />\n唔知係唔係因為個場細，音響比較震撼<br />\n同isquare一樣都係5.1聲道"},{"pid":"85f244e4d00a31375991a4d26bcb46a3a2fcf26e","tid":334471,"uid":4607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:14:06.000Z","msg":"坐邊幾行好d？<br />\n第一次睇imax唔識預位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b80ce65f2602bf9b5dfe1b4e1b83a22051b6f4","tid":334471,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐邊幾行好d？<br />\n第一次睇imax唔識預位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間就j，側少少就k"},{"pid":"97d739a0851b257661e56165b07f599aa9c02cf1","tid":334471,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身住元朗, 以前新元朗中心仲有百老匯個陣都完全唔會想係元朗睇戲<br />\n<br />\n元朗睇戲的人質素係極差, <br />\n<br />\n大聲傾計, 傾電話, 依D 野係以前係層出不窮<br />\n<br />\n當然, 近年多左新樓, 多左外面D 人搬入來會變成點真係唔知</blockquote><br />\n同意 無乜必要都唔想係元朗睇<br />\n雖然香港人普遍都叫無品 係好多區睇戲都被搔擾過<br />\n但零零舍舍係啲牛屎佬未撚進化咁 額頭擺明寫住賤格兩個字</blockquote><br />\n星期六睇完早場，70蚊平撚到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇野喎，全場觀眾都幾靜下，同去isquare機場睇差唔多<br />\n同埋座位夠闊，行與行之間有好多空位，伸直對腳都踢唔到前面張櫈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係細佬想踢凳佢隻腳都唔撚夠長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n硬件一流，觀眾質素就真係睇彩數<br />\n慶幸上星期五睇期間相安無事"}]}